                                        <span class="opacity:50"><span class="tracking:tight">Your favorite tech company</span> <span class="tracking:tight"><span class="space:nowrap">is built</span> on authenticity and</span> <span class="space:nowrap">highly performant</span> design,</span> <span class="space:nowrap">not marketing hacks.</span>
